Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.02,0:00:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底要昏睡到何时?绫小路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.96,0:00:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道你要让恐怖的天使降临吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.40,0:02:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.07,0:02:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我到底是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.34,0:02:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救救我   我需要你的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.08,0:02:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了 你终于醒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.22,0:02:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.23,0:02:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弥海儿 弥海儿?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.96,0:02:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是...我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.53,0:03:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“ACADEMY”的基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.20,0:03:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ACADEMY!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.94,0:03:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我把你带来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.64,0:03:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们需要你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.91,0:03:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了将久留美的ANGEL
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.71,0:03:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,HEART． 改给停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.42,0:03:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人，你在哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.96,0:03:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人，快出来唷  主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.67,0:03:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到仲人先生了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.44,0:03:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，四处斩没看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.80,0:03:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗...找不到...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.57,0:03:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在做什么呢?蠢材久留美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.64,0:03:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是和他在一起吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.65,0:03:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然还敢说仲人先生是属于你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.78,0:03:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.88,0:03:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别这样，卡铃加!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.72,0:03:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是仲人先生失踪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.72,0:03:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算责备你的姊姊也于究无补
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.92,0:03:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.13,0:03:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是久留美不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.63,0:04:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我一直留在他的身边就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.46,0:04:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美...应该怎么做才好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.10,0:04:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们这样找，都找不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.14,0:04:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且仲人也不是那种
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.74,0:04:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随随便便什么都不讲就离开的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.54,0:04:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许是...    啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.71,0:04:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仲人先生也许是被
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.35,0:04:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ACADEMY的人给带走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.68,0:04:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.82,0:04:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ACADEMY
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.36,0:04:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前不久我看到左方有道光线闪过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.99,0:04:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不像是流星，是一种奇怪的光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.16,0:04:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想仲人先生是被
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.97,0:04:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ACADEMY的人带走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.50,0:04:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.44,0:04:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们到底把他带到那里去了呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.07,0:04:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.68,0:04:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要将ANGELHEART改
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.71,0:04:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给停止?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.81,0:04:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只要叫久留美合作就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.65,0:04:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为久留美最听你的话了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.12,0:05:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之后呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.49,0:05:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会从久留美的身体里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.06,0:05:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,取出ANGEL. HEART改
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.03,0:05:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放到其他地方去保管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.86,0:05:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从身体里面取出...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.00,0:05:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样做的话，久留美小姐会死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.87,0:05:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说她会死...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.74,0:05:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也是ACADEMY的人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.87,0:05:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们是因为要做什么坏事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.77,0:05:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而久留美是你们最大的阻碍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.48,0:05:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才...  怎么可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.98,0:05:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正好相反
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.38,0:05:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么做，也是为了久留美好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.25,0:05:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了久留美好...什么意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.42,0:05:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道ANGELHEART
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.32,0:05:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是什么东西吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.89,0:05:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ANGELHEART
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.43,0:05:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了得到超越科学的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.83,0:05:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它把天使的力量给封印住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.50,0:05:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将天使的力量...封印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.34,0:05:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,钢铁天使不是普通的机械公仔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.54,0:05:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为这个原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.24,0:06:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是却有人对现状还不满足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.82,0:06:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是你所认识的绫小路博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.32,0:06:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博士为了制造出更强的钢铁天使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.92,0:06:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将ANGELHEART改良
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.72,0:06:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,制造出ANGELHEART改
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.63,0:06:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是那却是一个禁断的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.20,0:06:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,禁断的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.07,0:06:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,改里面的力量不只是天使力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.51,0:06:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道还有其他吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.68,0:06:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是恶魔的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.18,0:06:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恶魔!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.18,0:06:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么!那个叫仲人的少年被抓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.09,0:06:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，非常抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.19,0:06:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在他的身边却发生这种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.46,0:06:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有敌人的情报吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.49,0:06:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌人的目的到现在还不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.70,0:06:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是好像和带走绫小路博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.20,0:06:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是同一个集团的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.90,0:07:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天城，好像有什么大事情要开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.21,0:07:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你别想骗我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.05,0:07:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我讲的都是事实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.21,0:07:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你骗人，久留美小姐的心里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.45,0:07:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能隐藏着恶魔的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.99,0:07:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果她被恶魔的力量占领
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.19,0:07:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后果就不堪设想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.66,0:07:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世界也许因此而灭亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.06,0:07:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.40,0:07:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想变成那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.33,0:07:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是这样继续下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.77,0:07:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恶魔的翅膀一定会展开的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.74,0:07:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恶魔的翅膀被展开...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.15,0:07:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算被恶魔的力量占领
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.65,0:07:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美小姐也不会变成那种人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.55,0:07:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果服从的回路失效了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.29,0:07:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美就不会再是久留美了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.26,0:07:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就因为这样，要久留美小姐死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.93,0:07:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这点我做不到!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.20,0:08:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来你真的那么喜欢久留美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.61,0:08:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,钢铁天使并不需要爱情的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.95,0:08:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她只是被制造出来的物品啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.28,0:08:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,物品...物品没有死亡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.79,0:08:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不是物品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.19,0:08:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美小姐会哭会笑，也会生气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.73,0:08:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是物品...是物品...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.60,0:08:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就不会有那种情绪发生的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.60,0:08:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身为物品却自认是人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.77,0:08:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太悲惨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.71,0:08:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准这样讲久留美小姐!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.24,0:08:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你那么喜欢她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.95,0:08:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许你更应该亲手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.38,0:08:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将ANGELHEART改
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.42,0:08:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给停止啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.15,0:08:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道你想静静的看着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.55,0:08:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美变成恶魔?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.39,0:08:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会给你时间考虑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.14,0:09:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要留在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.65,0:09:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许将来博士会再回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.15,0:09:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们一定会把博士给救出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.49,0:09:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有主人也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.99,0:09:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美，你要记得你和他的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.06,0:09:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以拯救人类的未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.43,0:09:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.61,0:09:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天城博士，我们来接你们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.94,0:09:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们就是将军所讲的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.28,0:09:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是吉祥寺   我是小金井
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.95,0:09:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将军命令我们要与你们同行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.95,0:10:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经安排军用机在机场了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.66,0:10:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.06,0:10:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了，拜托你们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.21,0:11:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她那么天真无邪的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.88,0:11:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天真 无邪 活泼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.35,0:11:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本就像天使使一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.98,0:11:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能会是恶魔呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.92,0:11:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美小姐...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.66,0:11:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,情况如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.80,0:11:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.30,0:11:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是要他答应配合我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.80,0:11:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许会有点困难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.01,0:12:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗...最坏的打算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.14,0:12:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你应该知道吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.11,0:12:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.13,0:12:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.74,0:12:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“那是骗人的!”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.24,0:14:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小金井，虽然很久没做预告了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.84,0:14:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是气氛好像和以前大不相同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.17,0:14:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前那些欢笑声不再有了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.84,0:14:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,次回  钢铁天久留美第19话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.28,0:14:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“突入!ACADEMY基地”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.85,0:14:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小金井   什么事?吉祥寺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.46,0:14:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然好久没做预告了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.83,0:14:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是好像和以前大不相同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.83,0:14:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，以前那些欢笑声到哪去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.10,0:14:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我觉得好寂寞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.47,0:14:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能!别的节目不谈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.94,0:14:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有这个节目绝不可能发生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.97,0:14:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,次回  钢铁天使久留美第19话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.04,0:14:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“突入!ACADEMY基地”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.35,0:15:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请保持室内光亮，和电视距离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.42,0:15:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天城博士  你是哪位?
